      <p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_eb8fb429-17a8-474e-8a1b-cc69a11a7f49" id="_eb8fb429-17a8-474e-8a1b-cc69a11a7f49"></a>Cloud Security Alliance</p>
      <p style="text-align:left;" align="left" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_cea37e8d-1eec-4629-a8ff-a7521e902c23" id="_cea37e8d-1eec-4629-a8ff-a7521e902c23"></a>
